statements: SELECT user_id, access_time, access_type, fingerprint_scan_status FROM user_access_logs
SELECT access_time, user_id, access_type, fingerprint_scan_status FROM user_access_logs
SELECT access_type, access_time, user_id, fingerprint_scan_status FROM user_access_logs
SELECT * FROM user_access_logs
SELECT user_id, access_type, access_time FROM user_access_logs ORDER BY access_time DESC
SELECT user_id, access_time, access_type, fingerprint_scan_status FROM user_access_logs WHERE user_id = 123 ORDER BY access_time DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT access_time, access_type FROM user_access_logs WHERE access_type = 'LOGIN' ORDER BY access_time ASC;
SELECT user_id, access_type FROM user_access_logs WHERE access_time > '2022-01-01' AND fingerprint_scan_status = 'SUCCESS' ORDER BY access_time ASC, user_id DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT COUNT(*), access_type FROM user_access_logs GROUP BY access_type HAVING COUNT(*) > 1 ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC;

SELECT user_id, access_time FROM user_access_logs WHERE access_type = 'login';
SELECT scanner_id, COUNT(*) AS total_scans FROM unauthorized_scans GROUP BY scanner_id ORDER BY total_scans DESC;
SELECT access_type, COUNT(*) AS total_access FROM user_access_logs WHERE access_time >= '2022-01-01' GROUP BY access_type;
SELECT ual.user_id, ua.scan_result FROM user_access_logs AS ual LEFT JOIN unauthorized_scans AS ua ON ual.scanner_id = ua.scanner_id WHERE ual.access_time >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM user_access_logs ORDER BY access_time DESC, user_id ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT user_id, count(*) as total_accesses FROM user_access_logs GROUP BY user_id HAVING total_accesses > 5
